About.Name: Name: Sangraal
About.WhatIdo: What I do: I am a freelance artist that specilizes in drawing everyday objects and scenery.
About.Vision: Vision: I believe that working with clients is the key to success, I aim to work with my clients at every step of the creation process to ensure that the products created are exactly what the customer is looking for
